{"tid":2408871,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"以色列調查接種輝瑞疫苗 有症狀個案降94%","createTime":"2021-02-15T10:15:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-16T03:07:41.000Z","uid":41343,"like":124,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"4c9aba52caadf59bb90d462108651816cf7124cb","tid":2408871,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T10:15:01.000Z","msg":"以色列最大衞生機構Clalit披露，根據6萬名接種兩劑輝瑞新冠疫苗的民眾的分析結果，該等人士感染新冠病毒及有症狀的比率減少94%。同時，該群體內發展成為嚴重症況的比率也下降92%。<br />\n<br />\n有關結果是對比6萬名沒有接種的民眾而得出。<br />\n<br />\nClalit首席創意主管Ran Balicer表示，調查顯示，輝瑞新冠疫苗是可有效預防疫情擴散。他又表示，數據反映，接種第二劑疫苗後的兩周後，預防率更高。"},{"pid":"0718029ff49ec67d4eff34af8bf58a073061ef1a","tid":2408871,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T10:15:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2712657/all\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2712657%2Fall&d=lQL0ZJWU6LWL4dZDafr4eTQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=e64dedde\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2712657/all</a>"},{"pid":"03524c2d8ba27ec4ee98b4cf21b1b350d220dd71","tid":2408871,"uid":76804,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T10:16:43.000Z","msg":"美國好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b6c2197356a37174f894ea5b6d573dea00b84e7","tid":2408871,"uid":25468,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T10:17:52.000Z","msg":"即係有用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d0dbd956ac99ad5b3c2113a514f90ae2b1dc3ca","tid":2408871,"uid":129664,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T10:20:30.000Z","msg":"持續下降中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4vyFyH7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4vyFyH7.png&h=e748e9d0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"debf892ca4c151b4f4c4779044a6